      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is super busy and i feel like i'm just waiting forever for an appointment when i'm feeling like this right now. if i just tapered off the zoloft slowly on my own and then started the st johns wort supplement, wouldn't that be okay? i just want to move away from the synthetic stuff and try something more holistic since the side effects are so bad.",
